@node MAIN
@title "Padlock Docs - ©1995 Iain L. King"

   Padlock is a small utility that I programmed in Blitz Basic 2.  I was
trying to get the hang of the intuition commands, and decided to make a
locking program like this because :

               A: It would not take long to implement the basic code, and
               B: I'm sure I had a B when I started.

  So  @{" What is Padlock? " link WHATSIT}
      @{" How do I use it? " link HOWUSE}
      @{" What problems could I have with it? " link PROBS}
      @{" So how does it work then, I mean really? " link HOWWORK}
      @{" Any extra features? " link FEATURES}
      @{" What versions have there been? " link VERSION}
      @{" Will there be any more then?" link MORE}
  And @{" Do I really want to see the credits then? " link CREDITS}

   I suppose I'd better write a disclaimer.

   I will not be held responsible for any damage caused by this program (I
